{"id":170,"parent_id":158,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":170,"title":"2 Corinthians 12","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 12"],[".studySummary",["i","Paul is caught up to the third heaven—The Lord gives men weaknesses that they may triumph over them—Paul manifests the signs of an Apostle."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.1","order":"03.10.012.19212"},["b","1"],"It is not expedient for me doubtless to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"glory"],". I will come to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"visions"],"and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"revelations"],"of the Lord."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.2","order":"03.10.012.19213"},["b","2"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"I"],"knew a man in Christ above fourteen years ago, (whether in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"body"],", I cannot tell; or whether out of the body, I cannot tell: God knoweth;) such an one caught up to the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"third"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"heaven"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.3","order":"03.10.012.19214"},["b","3"],"And I knew such a man, (whether in the body, or out of the body, I cannot tell: God knoweth;)"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.4","order":"03.10.012.19215"},["b","4"],"How that he was caught up into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"paradise"],", and heard",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"unspeakable"],"words, which it is",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"not"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"lawful"],"for a man to utter."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.5","order":"03.10.012.19216"},["b","5"],"Of such an one will I glory: yet of myself I will not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"glory"],", but in mine infirmities."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.6","order":"03.10.012.19217"},["b","6"],"For though I would desire to glory, I shall not be a fool; for I will say the truth: but",["i","now"],"I forbear, lest any man should think of me above that which he seeth me",["i","to be,"],"or",["i","that"],"he heareth of me."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.7","order":"03.10.012.19218"},["b","7"],"And lest I should be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"exalted"],"above measure through the abundance of the revelations, there was given to me a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"thorn"],"in the flesh, the messenger of Satan to buffet me, lest I should be exalted above measure."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.8","order":"03.10.012.19219"},["b","8"],"For this thing I besought the Lord thrice, that it might depart from me."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.9","order":"03.10.012.19220"},["b","9"],"And he said unto me, My",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"grace"],"is sufficient for thee: for my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"strength"],"is made perfect in",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"weakness"],". Most gladly therefore will I rather glory in my infirmities, that the power of Christ may",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"rest"],"upon me."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.10","order":"03.10.012.19221"},["b","10"],"Therefore I take pleasure in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"infirmities"],", in reproaches, in necessities, in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"persecutions"],", in distresses for Christ’s sake: for when I am",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"weak"],", then am I",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"strong"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.11","order":"03.10.012.19222"},["b","11"],"I am become a fool in glorying; ye have compelled me: for I ought to have been commended of you: for in nothing am I behind the very",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"chiefest"],"apostles, though I be nothing."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.12","order":"03.10.012.19223"},["b","12"],"Truly the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"signs"],"of an apostle were wrought among you in all patience, in signs, and wonders, and mighty deeds."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.13","order":"03.10.012.19224"},["b","13"],"For what is it wherein ye were inferior to other churches, except",["i","it be"],"that I myself was not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"burdensome"],"to you? forgive me this wrong."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.14","order":"03.10.012.19225"},["b","14"],"Behold, the third time I am ready to come to you; and I will not be burdensome to you: for I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"seek"],"not yours, but you: for the children ought not to lay up for the parents, but the parents for the children."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.15","order":"03.10.012.19226"},["b","15"],"And I will very gladly spend and be spent for you; though the more abundantly I love you, the less I be loved."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.16","order":"03.10.012.19227"},["b","16"],"But be it so, I did not burden you: nevertheless, being crafty, I caught you with guile."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.17","order":"03.10.012.19228"},["b","17"],"Did I make a gain of you by any of them whom I sent unto you?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.18","order":"03.10.012.19229"},["b","18"],"I desired Titus, and with",["i","him"],"I sent a brother. Did Titus make a gain of you? walked we not in the same spirit?",["i","walked we"],"not in the same steps?"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.19","order":"03.10.012.19230"},["b","19"],"Again, think ye that we excuse ourselves unto you? we speak before God in Christ: but",["i","we do"],"all things, dearly beloved, for your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"edifying"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.20","order":"03.10.012.19231"},["b","20"],"For I fear, lest, when I come, I shall not find you such as I would, and",["i","that"],"I shall be found unto you such as ye would not: lest",["i","there be"],"debates, envyings, wraths,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"strifes"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"backbitings"],", whisperings, swellings,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"tumults"],":"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.21","order":"03.10.012.19232"},["b","21"],["i","And"],"lest, when I come again, my God will humble me among you, and",["i","that"],"I shall bewail many which have sinned already, and have not repented of the uncleanness and fornication and lasciviousness which they have committed."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.1a","order":"03.10.012.19233"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/boast"},"TG Boast"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.1b","order":"03.10.012.19235"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.1"},"1 Cor. 9:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.1c","order":"03.10.012.19237"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/revelation"},"TG Revelation"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.2a","order":"03.10.012.19239"},["b","2a"],["span.small","GR"],"I know a man in Christ who fourteen years ago."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.2b","order":"03.10.012.19241"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/137.1"},"D&C 137:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.2c","order":"03.10.012.19243"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/celestial-glory"},"TG Celestial Glory"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.2d","order":"03.10.012.19245"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heaven"},"TG Heaven"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.4a","order":"03.10.012.19247"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/paradise"},"TG Paradise"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.4b","order":"03.10.012.19249"},["b","4b"],["span.small","GR"],"ineffable."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.4c","order":"03.10.012.19251"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.17"},"3 Ne. 17:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.34.32-34"},"19:34 (32–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.4d","order":"03.10.012.19253"},["b","4d"],["span.small","GR"],"possible, permitted."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.5a","order":"03.10.012.19255"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/boast"},"TG Boast"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.7a","order":"03.10.012.19257"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/3.4"},"D&C 3:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.7b","order":"03.10.012.19259"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pain"},"TG Pain"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.9a","order":"03.10.012.19261"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.9b","order":"03.10.012.19263"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strength"},"TG Strength"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.9c","order":"03.10.012.19265"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.9"},"2 Cor. 13:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.27.26-28"},"Ether 12:27 (26–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.9d","order":"03.10.012.19267"},["b","9d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.12"},"D&C 39:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.10a","order":"03.10.012.19269"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/adversity"},"TG Adversity"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.10b","order":"03.10.012.19271"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/persecution"},"TG Persecution"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.10c","order":"03.10.012.19273"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/humility"},"TG Humility"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.10d","order":"03.10.012.19275"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.10"},"Joel 3:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/50.16"},"D&C 50:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.11a","order":"03.10.012.19277"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.1"},"1 Cor. 9:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.12a","order":"03.10.012.19279"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/signs"},"TG Signs"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.13a","order":"03.10.012.19281"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/11.9.8-9"},"2 Cor. 11:9 (8–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.14a","order":"03.10.012.19283"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/10.33"},"1 Cor. 10:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.19a","order":"03.10.012.19285"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/14.26"},"1 Cor. 14:26"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/edification"},"TG Edification"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.20a","order":"03.10.012.19287"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strife"},"TG Strife"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.20b","order":"03.10.012.19289"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/backbiting"},"TG Backbiting"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.20c","order":"03.10.012.19291"},["b","20c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rioting-and-reveling"},"TG Rioting and Reveling"],"."]]}
